  "texts": [
    "However, retrieving information from this enormous knowledge base is cumbersome and time-consuming.",
    "Thus, text summarization is a potential solution to this information overload problem.",
    "Text summarization condenses this information for quick and efficient consumption.Text summarization is the art of condensing lengthy textual documents into concise versions while retaining the original document's core meaning and informational value.",
    "Doing so results in more digestible and easily comprehensible documents to the reader.",
    "This process facilitates the efficient handling of extensive documents."
